trader participation and market psychology.
  

201
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:59,440
When price breaks a support zone, it 
transforms into potential future resistance. 

202
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:05,600
This reveals the market's internal memory.
Well, professional traders understand markets  

203
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:09,280
